FBIS4-40790 "drsov119__a94039" FBIS-SOV-94-119-A Daily Report 21 June 1994 ANNEX Ukraine Development of Russian-Ukrainian Border Area Discussed Development of Russian-Ukrainian Border Area Discussed LD1706200694 Moscow RIA in English 1607 GMT 17 Jun 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY LD1706200694 Moscow RIA English BFN [Text] Bryansk, June 17, RIA -- Issues pertaining to the development of the Russo-Ukrainian order were discussed in Bryansk by the regional administration, Colonel Viktor Mishchenko, chief of staff of the Western Group of Frontier Forces of Russia, and Sergey Bekov, deputy chairman of the State Customs Committee. They discussed the creation of check-points and collaboration of the customs personnel and frontier guards at check-points in Troebortny and Yurkovichiy, said Vladimir Karpov, head of the Bryansk region administration.
